POLICIES
The Sneak. Philosophy
We're devoted to two things: hot sneakers and awesome customer service.

We try to make every part of the buying experience seamless and convenient, and your satisfaction will always be our first and only priority.

This means:
  • We're accurate in our item listings, so you know what you're getting
  • We ship when we say we'll ship
  • We respond to messages quickly and professionally
Shipping
We ship Australia Post, and provide tracking for each package, which we'll communicate to you after dispatch.

Shipment takes place the next business day after payment is received.

Want to do a pick-up?Check the listing to see if pick-ups are optioned.
Returns
Don't like it? Don't worry.

We offer 30-day returns, so you're covered; you can return the item you purchased for exchange or refund at any point in that time frame. If you're returning for a refund, please be aware we refund the purchase price but not the original or return shipping. If you didn't pay a separate shipping cost, we'll refund the purchase price.

Since we need to be able to sell the item to someone else, the item needs to be in its original condition and with its original box/packaging, tissue paper, tags, etc.

For international buyers, please check the item listing for return conditions.

Changed your mind after checkout? Contact us as quickly as possible so we can help get your order cancelled.
International Buyers
We ship to other countries on an item-by-item basis, with the exception of the EU and EEA areas, to which we do not ship.

Please check the listing for information regarding the countries the item ships to.

International duties/customs/taxes/other fees: some countries levy charges when you import an item - buyers are responsible for paying these charges, so please check with your nation's relevant government department or authority.
Pricing
We strive to price competitively, but we're always open to negotiating. If you're looking for a better deal, contact us and we'll see what we can do.
Feedback
Like other independent ebay sellers, we thrive on positive feedback, which highlights a seller's integrity to potential buyers. Our commitment to our buyers is the same - we always leave positive feedback after a good selling experience as a measure of our appreciation.

If you purchase from us and you feel we've fallen short in any way, please contact us before leaving negative feedback. We hate seeing a buyer end up dissatisfied with their purchase, and we'll go the extra mile to make it right.
